com.igeekinc.luwak

Class FUSEDispatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.igeekinc.luwak.FUSEDispatch
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinuxFUSEDispatch, OSXFUSEDispatch

    public abstract class FUSEDispatch
extends java.lang.Object
    FUSEDispatch reads messages from the FUSE device and dispatches them on some number of dispatch threads. The received messages are passed to a FUSELowLevel which processes them and returns appropriate messages.
    Author:
    David L. Smith-Uchida
